{"title": "How do I Add Pension, HCC or DVA Numbers?", "body": "Follow these steps to add Pension, HCC or DVA numbers to a patient record:\nOpen the Patient Record\nNavigate to the Details tab\nClick Settings\nNavigate to the PENSION/HCC heading\nUpdate the form with all the required details\nClick Save to apply the changes\nThe patient's pension, HCC or DVA numbers have now been updated"}